speaker.name: Pranjal Biyani
speaker.biography: Pranjal is an experienced AI Scientist building the first AI powered platform to accelerate R&D for Material Sciences across the globe. He loves opening black-box models to reveal insightful AI secrets that help decision makers adapt with the ever changing Industry needs. He also loves to teach and mentor passionate individuals aspiring to be a part of the Data Science Community, all with his favourite language, Python!
